name: Dwarf on a chest of gold
description: The first digitized exhibition of the master of pottery, Ivan Ivanovich Loboichenko. Ivan Ivanovich Loboychenko created this work 10 years ago. He wanted to make a collection of gnomes, there are 25 of them in the collection. Options: Height - 330 mm Width - 110 mm Length - 190 mm Material - clay, Manufacturing process - carving, molding, mashing, watering.
